author: apivovarov
message:
[TF]Remove unused Kokkos mdspan dependency from raft.

The `@kokkos//:mdspan` dependency is not needed because raft project has its own copy of mdspan in cpp/include/raft/thirdparty/mdspan

PiperOrigin-RevId: 806025730

files.patch:
@@ -19,7 +19,6 @@ load("@local_xla//third_party/gpus:sycl_configure.bzl", "sycl_configure")
 load("@local_xla//third_party/highwayhash:workspace.bzl", highwayhash = "repo")
 load("@local_xla//third_party/hwloc:workspace.bzl", hwloc = "repo")
 load("@local_xla//third_party/implib_so:workspace.bzl", implib_so = "repo")
-load("@local_xla//third_party/kokkos:workspace.bzl", kokkos = "repo")
 load("@local_xla//third_party/llvm:workspace.bzl", llvm = "repo")
 load("@local_xla//third_party/nanobind:workspace.bzl", nanobind = "repo")
 load("@local_xla//third_party/nasm:workspace.bzl", nasm = "repo")
@@ -84,7 +83,6 @@ def _initialize_third_party():
     kissfft()
     libprotobuf_mutator()
     libwebp()
-    kokkos()
     ml_dtypes()
     nanobind()
     nasm()
